WITH pre_top_n as (
    select CASE 
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Partner Widget'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Type operation'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.TYPE
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Accepted Transaction'
            THEN to_char(TRANSACTIONS.CONFIRMED)
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Crypto currency'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.currency
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Fiat currency'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.fiat_currency
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Country card'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.CARD_ISOCOUNTRY
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Geoscheme card'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.CARD_GEOSCHEME
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Brand card'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.CARD_BRAND
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Pay System'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.PAY_SYSTEM
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Country IP'
            THEN COUNTRY_CODES.COUNTRY_NAME_EN
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Geoscheme IP'
            THEN COUNTRY_CODES.GEOSCHEME_BUSINESS
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Acquirer'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.vendor_name
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Network'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.Network
            END AS GROUP_BY
         , row_number() over (order by sum(TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) desc) as rn
    from MART.TRANSACTIONS
    left join MD.COUNTRY_CODES
                   on lower(TRANSACTIONS.LOCATION_COUNTRY) = lower(COUNTRY_CODES.COUNTRY_CODE_ALPHA_3)
    where {{CREATED_AT}} and
      {{CREATED_AT}} and {{partner_name}} and
          {{crypto_currency}} and {{fiat_currency}} and 
          {{pay_system}}  and {{LOCATION_COUNTRY}} and {{LOCATION_GEO}} and
          {{network}} and {{flag_is_recurring}}  and {{is_user_based_selective}} and
          {{IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC}} and {{AUTH_TYPE}} and {{RETRY_EXCLUDE}} and {{is_amount_based_selective}} 
          and VENDOR_NAME = 'blik_hyperion_mobilum'
    group by 1
    order by 2 desc),
     top_n as (
         select GROUP_BY
                , CASE WHEN rn < {{top_n}}
                    THEN GROUP_BY
                    ELSE 'others' END AS top_n_parameter
         from pre_top_n
     ),
  main_query as (select TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT 
                      , top_n.top_n_parameter
                      , TRANSACTIONS.TURNOVER_EUR
                      , TRANSACTIONS.id
                      , TRANSACTIONS.confirmed
      from mart.TRANSACTIONS 
      left join MD.COUNTRY_CODES
                   on lower(TRANSACTIONS.LOCATION_COUNTRY) = lower(COUNTRY_CODES.COUNTRY_CODE_ALPHA_3)
      left join top_n on top_n.GROUP_BY = CASE 
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Partner Widget'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.WIDGET_PARTNER_NAME
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Type operation'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.TYPE
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Accepted Transaction'
            THEN to_char(TRANSACTIONS.CONFIRMED)
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Crypto currency'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.currency
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Fiat currency'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.fiat_currency
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Country card'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.CARD_ISOCOUNTRY
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Geoscheme card'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.CARD_GEOSCHEME
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Brand card'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.CARD_BRAND
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Pay System'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.PAY_SYSTEM
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Country IP'
            THEN COUNTRY_CODES.COUNTRY_NAME_EN
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Geoscheme IP'
            THEN COUNTRY_CODES.GEOSCHEME_BUSINESS
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Acquirer'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.vendor_name
        WHEN {{TRANSACTION_COLUMNS_GROUPBY}} = 'Network'
            THEN TRANSACTIONS.Network
            END
                
      where TRANSACTIONS.SOURCE_MAIN = 'widget' and
      {{CREATED_AT}} and {{partner_name}} and
          {{crypto_currency}} and {{fiat_currency}} and 
          {{pay_system}}  and {{LOCATION_COUNTRY}} and {{LOCATION_GEO}} and
          {{network}} and {{flag_is_recurring}}  and {{is_user_based_selective}} and
          {{IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC}} and {{AUTH_TYPE}} and {{RETRY_EXCLUDE}} and {{is_amount_based_selective}} 
          and VENDOR_NAME = 'blik_hyperion_mobilum'
      ) 
select date_trunc({{GRANULARITY}},CREATED_AT) as DT
      , top_n_parameter AS Parameter_topN
     , count(case when confirmed then id end)/count(*) as ar
from main_query
group by 1,2
order by 1,3 desc
